## Elixirs
#### Elixir of Clarity
*Potion, RARITY*





When imbibed before resting, there are two effects. First, the drinker receives 1 additional 1st-level spell slot and 1 additional 2nd-level spell slot when she prepares spells.




The next time you prepare spells within 24 hours of drinking this elixir, the number of spells you can prepare increases by 7 until you next finish a long rest. If you have multiple classes that allow you to prepare spells, you can distribute this increase among them as you choose.
   
Additionally, while your number of prepared spells is increased this way, you can change your prepared spells at any time by meditating for 1 minute for each spell you replace.


Upon drinking this elixir, choose 7 spells; they are known and prepared for you for the next 24 hours. You must be able to know or prepare a spell through one or more of your classes to be able to choose it. For the duration, you can spend 1 minute to replace 1 of those 7 spells as many times as you want, but must still respect any restrictions.


Upon drinking this elixir, you gain the ability to prepare an additional seven spells for the next 24 hours. If you have multiple sources of prepared spells, these spells can be from any combination of spell lists. While under the effects of this elixir, you can change your prepared spells at any time, spending at least 1 minute for each spell. This potion appears milky in nature, but when unstoppered, it rapidly turns perfectly clear.





